energy_kcal_method: ENERC - Energy (kcal/100 g EP) = total protein (g/100 g EP) x 4 + total fat (g/100 g EP) x 9 + available carbohydrate (g/100 g EP) x 4 + total dietary fibre (g/100 g EP) x 2 + alcohol (g/100 g EP) x 7
totalprotein_method: PROTCNT - Total protein (g/100 g EP) = nitrogen conversion factor (XN) × total nitrogen (g/100 g EP)
carbohydrates_method: <U+FEFF>CHOAVLDF Carbohydrate, available; calculated by difference (g/100 g EP) = 100 – (water + total fat + total protein + ash + total dietary fibre + alcohol) (g/100 g EP)
fibre_method: FIBTG - Total fiber (AOAC 991.43); FIBC -  if crude fiber reported []
folate_method: FOLDFE - Dietary folate equivalents (mcg/100 g EP) = naturally occurring food folates (mcg/100 g EP) + 1.7 × synthetic folic acid (mcg/100 g EP) - microbiological assay
folicacid_method: FOL - this values are presented between bracket [] - HPLC
vitaminb12_method: Mostly not reported, assumed to be HPLC, microbiological
vitamina_rae_method: VITA_RAE - Vitamin A in retinol equivalents (mcg/100 g EP) = retinol (mcg/100 g EP) + beta-carotene equivalents (mcg/100 g EP) / 6; RETOL - Retinol is analysed using HPLC
vitaminc_method: Various methods; sum of L-ascorbic acid (ASCL) and L-dehydroascorbic acid (ASCDL)
phyticacid_method: Calculated from phytate phosphorus by anion exchange method (AOAC 986.11) or [determined by direct precipitation] or [ determined by indirect precipitation]

totalprotein_method: <U+FEFF>PROTCNT - Total protein (g/100 g EP) = total nitrogen (g/100 g EP) x nitrogen conversion factor (XN); Nitrogen - <U+FEFF>ISO 5983-2 (Kjeldhal Method)

energy_kcal_method:
ENERC - Calc. from energy-yielding components FAT, CHOAVLDF, PROTCNT, FIBTG (<U+FEFF>Equation 2. Energy (kcal/100 g EP) = total protein (g/100 g EP) x 4 + total fat (g/100 g EP) x 9)
+ available carbohydrates (g/100 g EP) x 4 + dietary fibre (g/100 g EP) x 2 + alcohol (g/100 g EP) x 7
totalprotein_method:
PROTCNT - Calc. from NT using nitrogen-to-protein factor 6.25 <U+FEFF>
Equation 3. Total protein (g/100 g EP) = total nitrogen (g/100 g EP) x 6.25) - Nitrogen - <U+FEFF>Kjeldahl method
carbohydrates_method:
CHOAVLDF - Calc. from proximates WATER, FAT, PROTCNT, ASH, FIBTG (<U+FEFF>Available carbohydrates by difference (g/100 g EP) = 100 - water (g/100 g EP) -total fat (g/100 g EP) - total protein (g/100 g EP) - total dietary fibre (g/100 g EP) - ash (g/100
g EP))
folate_method: FOLDFE - microbiological assay; Not preferred/improper tagnames: FOLSUM, sum of vitamers determined by HPLC; FOL-, method unknown or variable (marked with * in table).
vitamina_rae_method: VITA = Total vitamin A activity expressed as Retinol Equivalent (RE) (mcg/100 g EP) = retinol + 1/6 mcg beta - carotene + 1/12 mcg a-carotene + 1/12 mcg beta-cryptoxanthin ; VITA_RAE = <U+FEFF>Total vitamin A activity expressed as Retinol Activity Equivalent (RAE) (mcg/100 g EP) = mcg retinol + 1/12 mcg beta- carotene + 1/24 mcg a-carotene + 1/24 mcg beta-cryptoxanthin
phyticacid_method: IP3; IP4; IP5; IP6; Not preferred tagnames: PHYTCPPD, phytic acid, determined by direct preciptation; PHYTCPP, phytic acid, calc. from phytate phosphorus, anion exchange method; PHYTPPI, Phytate, determined by indirect preciptation
